      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to a 7,900 RPM redline. The individual throttle bodies provide razor-sharp response, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the M Variable Differential Lock remains tight, providing excellent mechanical grip. While the exterior shows honest patina, the suspension bushings have been refreshed and the engine pulls strongly with no hesitation. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance icon optimized for the spirited enthusiast.",
